                <!--project 2 header-->
                <h2>Grade Book project</h2>
                <p>In Object Oriented Programming, I created python code that would emulate a teachers gradebook for a 
                    student. In this code, you could create a student by making their student id and linking it with their 
                    name, then you can enroll them into a class and enter a grade for them. My code also wouldnt let you 
                    enroll a student for a class that they were already in, as well as it won't let you enter a grade for 
                    a student that wasn't in a certian class, or didn't exist.
                </p>
            </article>
