                <h3>AI Chatbot Report Draft</h3>
                <p>I wrote a report draft as if I were working for Meta (aka Facebook and Instagram), proposing the idea of 
                    using AI chatbots to more efficiently deal with customer service and fix long wait times. My final report 
                    evaluates Rule-Based AI, Machine Learning AI, and Hybrid AI-Human chatbot models. My recommendation was to 
                    use Hybrid AI-Human chatbot models due to their low operational costs and due to Hybrid models being the 
                    most efficient in responding to customers.
                </p>
